@resource(aws.acm.Certificate, CumuliServerCertificate)
Name: cumuli-server-acm-certificate
Domain name: app.{domain_name}
Validation method: DNS

@resource(aws.route53.Record, CumuliValidationRecord)
In $CumuliHostedZone
The name, type and records are derived from the $CumuliServerCertificate domain validation option.
Ttl: 300

@resource(aws.acm.CertificateValidation, CumuliCertificateValidation)
For $CumuliServerCertificate, using $CumuliValidationRecord